and labeled it as such, and provide images of the habitus, male genitalia, and labels of that specimen (
<figureCitation box="[584,664,1510,1536]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1988,2013]" captionTargetBox="[174,1418,600,1936]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1435,561,1963]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 2. Hydrochus corruscans Bruch, habitus and male genitalia of lectotype." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3557931" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3557931/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="152">Figs. 2</figureCitation>
