<figureCitation box="[949,1055,1510,1536]" captionStart="FIGURES 12" captionStartId="15.[151,264,1980,2005]" captionTargetBox="[215,1415,381,1942]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[158,1430,381,1955]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURES 12A–E. Labels of lectotypes. (A) Hydrochus ducalis Knisch; (B) Hydrochus drakei Knisch; (C) Hydrochus variabilis Knisch; (D) Hydrochus corruscans Bruch; (E) Hydrochus argutus Knisch." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3557951" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3557951/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="152">Fig. 12D</figureCitation>
): “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Bruch" authorityName="Bruch" authorityYear="1915" box="[1084,1413,1510,1537]" class="Insecta" family="Hydrochidae" genus="Hydrochus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="152" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="corruscans">Hydrochus corruscans Bruch</taxonomicName>
